            "last_activity_date": 1464857428,
            "creation_date": 1464857428,
            "body": "<p>You can cache the global Application context.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>myApplicationContext.getSharedPreferences(NOTIFICATION_ID\", MODE_PRIVATE)\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
